             was indicted for <rs id="t18150510-43-off260" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150510-43-off260" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150510-43-off260" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150510-43-cd261" type="crimeDate">14th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150510-43-off260 t18150510-43-cd261"></join>, a pair of silver tea-tongs, value 4 s. two silver cannister tops, value 24 s. a wine strainer, value 7 s. a mantle cloak, value 30 s. and an umbrella, value 2 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18150510-43-victim482" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Cairns
                        <interp inst="t18150510-43-victim482" type="surname" value="Cairns"></interp>
